data.description: Welcome to your future dream home! This stunning 2021-built residence, nestled on 0.34 acres, is a perfect blend of modern luxury and inviting warmth, showcasing 3,108 finished sq ft designed for making lasting memories.  As you step through the front door, the open floor plan welcomes you into a space bathed in natural light, creating an inviting atmosphere for both daily living and entertaining. The heart of the home is the spacious kitchen, complete with a large island, cabinets for days, pantry, built-in microwave, and all the amenities a chef could dream of. Picture gatherings around the fireplace in the living room, creating a cozy focal point for laughter and connection on chilly evenings.  This home is tailor-made for entertaining, with a finished basement featuring a full bathroom, offering a versatile space for games, movies, or even a guest retreat. The mudroom, conveniently connected to the 2-car garage, ensures a seamless transition from the outside world to your private haven.  Step outside and discover not only the beauty of your 0.34-acre property but also a community rich in amenities. Enjoy sunny days by the pool, explore winding walking trails, or challenge friends to a game of basketball on the community courts. And when it's time for practical matters, appreciate the convenience of being within 10 minutes of shopping.  Upstairs, discover four bedrooms, each offering ample space and comfort. The owner's suite is a true retreat with a private bathroom, and the great-sized laundry room with its own closet that adds an extra touch of convenience.  With thoughtful details like a tankless water heater, closets galore, and unfinished basement space for storage, this home combines functionality with style. Embrace the potential for customization and expansion in the unfinished space, tailoring it to your unique needs.  Don't miss the opportunity to call this house your home—a place where warmth, style, and the promise of countless memories await. Welcome to a lifetime of comfort and joy!
